Package com.toy_store.java.production

com.toy_store.java.production is a group classes that handle production elements, such as products, manufacturers, etc.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Manufacturer
    Class that represents a manufacturer for a specific product.
    Product
    Represents a product on the store.
    ProductBuilder
    Class that represents the builder for a Product.
  • Exception Summary
    Exception Description
    DuplicateProductException
    Exception thrown when the a product is being added to the store and it already exists.
    ManufacturerNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when a manufacturer is not found.
    NotEnoughItemsException
    Exception thrown when the user tries to calculate the total of a product with the quantity to low.
    ProductNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when a product is not found.
